thread.title: Westpac Banking Notes APRA Papers On Capital & Liquidity

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Westpac Banking Notes APRA Papers On Capital & Liquidity

organizations.name: westpac banking notes apra papers on capital & liquidity

text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Westpac Banking Corp:
* WESTPAC ACKNOWLEDGES APRA PAPERS ON CAPITAL & LIQUIDITY * AS AT DEC. 31 2017, WESTPAC‘S LEVERAGE RATIO WAS 5.5 PERCENT
* ‍IMPACT ON WESTPAC‘S RWA, CAPITAL RATIOS AND OTHER FINANCIAL RATIOS CANNOT YET BE ACCURATELY ASSESSED​
* ‍APRA HAS INDICATED THAT PROPOSED CHANGES MAY BE RECALIBRATED​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
